"""

def distinct_digits(n):
    """
    >>> distinct_digits(121)
    False
    >>> distinct_digits(123)
    True
    """
    n = str(n)
    for i in range(len(n)):
        for j in range(i+1, len(n)):
            if n[i] == n[j]:
                return False
    return True

def count_odd_distinct_digits():
    """
    >>> count_odd_distinct_digits()
    300
    """
    count = 0
    for i in range(100, 1000):
        if i % 2 == 1 and distinct_digits(i):
            count += 1
    return count
